{"tid":456272,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最佳航空公司排名榜　國泰大跌至第9位","createTime":"2017-11-02T23:59:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T04:00:43.000Z","uid":81228,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"31f90614c6ca6aab43195c59a529cc456cd89f1a","tid":456272,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171102/photo/bkn-20171102214545804-1102_00822_001_01b.jpg?20171102215730\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171102%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171102214545804-1102_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20171102215730&h=f201a050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰航空幾乎跌出10大排名榜。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空因管理不善，在全球最佳航空公司排名榜不斷下跌。<a href=\"http://網站AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99AirlineRatings.com&d=Hltc14%2F7mao1D6uueVlELk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4bea7df8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">網站AirlineRatings.com</a>公布2018年十大最佳航空公司排名，國泰由2017年的第4位大跌至第9位，險跌出十大排名榜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAirlineRatings.com&d=Hltc14%2F7mao1D6uueVlELk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a51abaf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AirlineRatings.com</a>根據13項準則來為航空公司排名，包括航空公司的安全紀錄、為乘客帶來舒適旅程的創意、乘客對航空公司的評價、機齡等。新西蘭航空連續第5年被評為全球最佳航空公司，第2位是澳洲航空，新加坡航空排第3位，維珍澳洲航空第4位，維珍航空第5位，第6位是阿堤哈德航空，全日空排第7，大韓航空居第8位，日航第10位。<br />\n<br />\n該網站表示，3間最佳航空公司都買了新飛機&mdash;&mdash;波音787和空中巴士A350，為其加分；又稱讚新西蘭航空財務表現出色、有創意、員工有動力，成為業界翹楚。<br />\n<br />\n10大最佳航空公司排名：<br />\n<br />\n1. 新西蘭航空<br />\n2. 澳洲航空<br />\n3. 新加坡航空<br />\n4. 維珍澳洲航空<br />\n5. 維珍航空<br />\n6. 阿堤哈德航空<br />\n7. 全日空<br />\n8. 大韓航空<br />\n9. 國泰航空<br />\n10. 日航<br />\n<br />\n(資料來源：<a href=\"http://AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAirlineRatings.com&d=Hltc14%2F7mao1D6uueVlELk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a51abaf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AirlineRatings.com</a>)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171102/bkn-20171102214545804-1102_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171102%2Fbkn-20171102214545804-1102_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=Hltc14%2F7mao1D6uueVlELk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=af770ce9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171102/bkn-20171102214545804-1102_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a>"},{"pid":"1b84bbd219797ecec393bdd508af0c10e319962e","tid":456272,"uid":144769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2436a8c108c7e84f34cee2b28555cace068b1853","tid":456272,"uid":137715,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:28:40.000Z","msg":"堅唔堅架個尼個排名 頭幾個都係澳紐航空"},{"pid":"49a74a659a157718529c7cab000366c3c0e67421","tid":456272,"uid":137717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.airlinequality.com/info/top-100-airlines-2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.airlinequality.com%2Finfo%2Ftop-100-airlines-2017%2F&d=Hltc14%2F7mao1D6uueVlELk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3b7bb26d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.airlinequality.com/info/top-100-airlines-2017/</a><br />\n<br />\nSkytrax排名同呢到差咁遠, 唔知信邊個好"},{"pid":"5d6cffbbf19fca978e2d312129561386af3d44e7","tid":456272,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T01:35:05.000Z","msg":"AWARD CATEGORY: Best Ultra-Low-Cost Airline<br />\n<a href=\"http://VietJetair.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FVietJetair.com&d=Hltc14%2F7mao1D6uueVlELk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b1924e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">VietJetair.com</a> wins Ultra-Low-Cost Airline <br />\n<br />\nA new award, taken out by Vietnam&rsquo;s <a href=\"http://VietJetAir.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FVietJetAir.com&d=